          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "UIKit uses this property and the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibarappearance/3198008-shadowcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to determine the shadow's appearance. When this property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the bar displays a default shadow tinted according to the value in the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibarappearance/3198008-shadowcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. If "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibarappearance/3198008-shadowcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or contains the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicolor/1621945-clearcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " color, the bar displays no shadow. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If this property contains a template image, the bar uses the image for the shadow and tints it using the value in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibarappearance/3198008-shadowcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibarappearance/3198008-shadowcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or contains the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicolor/1621945-clearcolor"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " color, the bar displays no shadow. However, if this property doesn't contain a template image, the bar displays the image without applying the shadow color. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
